        "title": "Challenge",
        "body": "1. Open the bridge lesson and describe what the example bridge imports and why the boundary matters.\\n2. Open the script lesson and explain why script behavior stays visible as a node instead of hiding in a registry.\\n3. Open the field lesson and explain why authored data belongs in a field instead of being smeared into declaration or presentation.\\n4. Say when you would choose an advanced primitive instead of a basic one.",
